uiEntry.title: header_bar_title_center
uiEntry.tooltip: On this panel you can view a character's personal details, traits and skills.||All of this is useful for judging a character and how best to use them.||Move your cursor over the different areas for more detail.

state.title: loyalty
state.tooltip: A general's loyalty affects how susceptible they are to bribes or defection.||Loyalty can be increased by promotion to office, becoming an heir or being married into the clan.||It can be lost by having these things taken from them or having a family member of theirs traded as a hostage.

state.title: honour
state.tooltip: A daimyo's honour affects the loyalty of his generals, his clan's fame and his diplomatic prowess.||Honour is gained through victories won personally by the daimyo.||Catastrophic battle losses and dishonourable actions will result in a loss of honour.

uiEntry.title: dy_attribute_title
uiEntry.tooltip: This shows the character's attribute in their chosen field.

uiEntry.title: rank_bar_fill
uiEntry.tooltip: This shows your character's rank, or expertise in their field.||A character's rank is increased as they gain experience through their actions.||At each new rank level, the character will be able to choose new skills from the skill tree.

uiEntry.title: button_advice
uiEntry.tooltip: Help||This button will take you to the in-game encyclopaedia.
